Class GreenhouseControls

java.lang.Object
Controller
GreenhouseControls
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class GreenhouseControls
extends Controller
The GreenhouseControls is the main Controller where all code is started once the user has selected an eventFile and booted the system. The code in this class is triggered by the GUI that it is associated with.
Author:
Craig Kubinec ID:3433193
See Also:
